  "content": "<!-- wp:group {\"newsletterVisibility\":\"email\",\"templateLock\":\"all\",\"align\":\"full\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"__BG_COLOR__\",\"text\":\"__TEXT_COLOR__\"}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull has-text-color has-background\" style=\"background-color:__BG_COLOR__;color:__TEXT_COLOR__;\">\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns are-vertically-aligned-center\"><!-- wp:column {\"templateLock\":\"all\",\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\",\"width\":\"50%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center\" style=\"flex-basis:50%\">__LOGO_OR_SITENAME__</div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"templateLock\":\"all\",\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\",\"width\":\"50%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center\" style=\"flex-basis:50%\">__SOCIAL_LINKS__</div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":\"16px\"} -->\n<div style=\"height:16px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Start your newsletter with an intro, sometimes known as a “topper”. This is where the lead writer or editor for the newsletter introduces the main storylines for the day.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":\"16px\"} -->\n<div style=\"height:16px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:newspack-newsletters/posts-inserter {\"postsToShow\":3,\"excerptLength\":20,\"innerBlocksToInsert\":[],\"featuredImageAlignment\":\"left\",\"featuredImageSize\":\"medium\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"newsletterVisibility\":\"email\",\"height\":\"16px\"} -->\n<div style=\"height:16px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"newsletterVisibility\":\"email\",\"align\":\"full\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"__BG_COLOR__\",\"text\":\"__TEXT_COLOR__\"},\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"40px\",\"right\":\"0px\",\"bottom\":\"40px\",\"left\":\"0px\"}}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull has-text-color has-background\" style=\"background-color:__BG_COLOR__;color:__TEXT_COLOR__;padding-top:40px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:40px;padding-left:0px\">\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 id=\"support-our-newsroom\">Support our newsroom</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Make sure you have a call-to-action to support your work. This can be a few sentences like this, reminding readers of the value of your newsroom, or it can be an image. Either way, make sure you give a clear CTA and a unique link to track support back to this email.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:buttons {\"layout\":{\"type\":\"flex\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons\"><!-- wp:button {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"__BG_COLOR__\",\"background\":\"__TEXT_COLOR__\"}},\"className\":\"is-style-fill\"} --><div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-fill\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-text-color has-background\" style=\"background-color:__TEXT_COLOR__;color:__BG_COLOR__\">Support us</a></div><!-- /wp:button --></div>\n<!-- /wp:buttons -->\n\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->"
}
